k?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=af807cb073c841dab484db825bddecc6&amp;amp;_e=N9i6kJulGAOonDstTkDXo9J1XinQDj4cVf1WTRCvpvJc7GcNFT86xVdJvyAfjvv7q5-NoUIcw0P1NcDyjpwf082ElsaSQsclyDswxYTeJD_yMzL2qUphc2MKB2-V2iafwko5XPYEeO16Gb4Ol9SJSw0OZIK0p6EOZ3lst0unSs2wf0be9llpbKtP7Ty5qAQzbzIXlZ6xHee02WiFFlSRnx4gdMWsfWGkpVIf0FvMPVQ%3D" target="_blank"&gt;前往仍在与山火作斗争的&lt;/a&gt;洛杉矶。加州州长加文·纽瑟姆将采取&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=af807cb073c841dab484db825bddecc6&amp;amp;_e=N9i6kJulGAOonDstTkDXoz5zALYxPMvp413E_TA5y3SQA2osr3cSGfuQM3Y1mEW9-osyhUpL2AUUcFaTThWVNGqsHWPB5OdcLF287yrZed87X4xMG4E5nV-WKnAWv1PJnnJpC3PD6W2y6UIBPmFtbHS6RREFju-GTyDM8RC_hsvskmEwf484JyBnv1XXhL1vOz6q7IbSMdOqjI1an2tND7pTFvUXfItdZqhUYxVdjvM%3D" target="_blank"&gt;微妙的平衡行动&lt;/a&gt;，因为他需要总统保留数十亿美元的救灾援助，尽管&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=af807cb073c841dab484db825bddecc6&amp;amp;_e=N9i6kJulGAOonDstTkDXo70Sd6peSwb5bXJRyHNAw1wWtcCQ_ubcdSAr1HluTnFRxk3TWzn-6DrbDgCnRb0sA30nL_HG8MZib3IeIIKxAKPseGqND1csgDYuLl3q5vA1lMmC6_51it0T6mLU3LaCHFkdL_Vj49hjui3kHPMbPM-hqhE0xmMdiuVI7SAVZ3QQefWebe4XTdV2m40zvHUP_R93e1YQcyPlcZrDgfXaCk0%3D" target="_blank"&gt;特朗普的行政命令&lt;/a&gt;明确针对接近该州进步理想的问题。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=af807cb073c841dab484db825bddecc6&amp;amp;_e=N9i6kJulGAOonDstTkDXo4vIyiEzMnGraZBr4PMa1Q1Uo_hrtKVhukSflQdqWB-Guw7seKNKypR6mf6jo6xGMTnp4pMEXW3VonpMQsx_9b_OzgRiJ8tOQr0ugnlq5mf5-A70HvR8vVW7iDngg46ZgKwzJBFgtVT9W-VT3sa4xL1XsAlL90X7ENj3F1JlsXHuQvM3h4oH8u6QTWtdlKKmWtFzlJeM8Uddoj2Z_zaCBeA%3D" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyCuO10W2994/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![