同时发出了额外的关税威胁。这次是针对欧盟国家，因为他告诉他们在美国生产商品，否则&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcSu_iVSp55uUdwY18gfunb46oZNU84pfyGpMXxi69c_obNWDWA-M11OqrcmMebRPVVeP7bv9Vr6DUdic-LlzdoCOL09lBz9-L6AeAFkX5QDJw-d8nnPw8oge0KTDq0tnSml8_tSrCIDvQVecr9kgwzuE-yKu-5KACdWyKaImzlMHANc5gCjLmmmRKWHhQ5TcI8IU8klNVCUGE1o5GLbEsxlZ_mynuK5ArhPsSNwMfVN10O9BY3PLwxxvKy1A8xqC8DUxhrIo-Tewk1VspiuRmUl2QGZklpAg8YvxQW2DNFenVAohafCV9A_MZtg2BV3GdQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;将面临处罚&lt;/a&gt;。尽管特朗普在上任第一天就推迟了对中国征收关税的核心竞选承诺，但他继续&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcTYEOEPpilFt6a9Zshbp6lXDhTNZtGuSAhOsriyZeaEwX0pkNoklKMdtPXOh-MB9HUV8xIYOnGPLU4kaZI8xUXHCfY3u2NUwobdIBpXLj7I9p4KuRS76Fgazhx6oI9tz5gVqLwVoX73UZqx5WWuR1SUSwSkIrDLdEH_tpQ6zbzq9ZcBZkBAMKhitFJufPoROpH0Lgetz1TLgYxbFcqjQvQ2mV0hAUU64BIjVkjxfkayYYOvsBJJlJMFq1o8yT5g7e9mVMtbbFxI0BP5dvo0iq2jKXyDLM_sc3DmqiZjy-_Bof7Qj0bzwBbKhLcWZLEdSWw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;威胁对加拿大和墨西哥征收25%的关税&lt;/a&gt;，这两个美国主要贸易伙伴已承诺迅速报复。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; 78 岁的特朗普出现在一段视频中，视频显示他的两侧是椭圆形办公室总统坚决办公桌上的一张特大印章图像。当他宣布将推动欧佩克削减原油价格时，他成功地&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgceFDE4DAvmQ0qZv8ykGkYBCkq9UuY_pCigrKg1u56bTauH-UD-lBABwmt0mtBSqv172NQtjadyqOwxGSZiGtlqlfZz34jc0Y2DzkKJWsSxPFPekSAXNq6GD7E1BfXBpazHuwoPy-rbWqexYnnRIKjuL_rLGOHbMgxgQbyNcSCq2CQMllajcxMFfucz0SPJ8cmDmzvVnj5QZTBc34ZojYwa522pzwzWOySIDVa2YtvGxWw6xfYX6RjHqcHS79aGAeiFYfLyBrkYUen8U0Ov-2wP6xdDPV7PCKY_WlHJgVPdxGvg56Hiqzf_K9ZSN7eObFIw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;压低了油价&lt;/a&gt;，尽管包括特朗普本人在内的早期总统的类似努力常常被置若罔闻。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcflPG3VOQTZQxO7M8hdLNCiLB04WgT2lKDFnaz9kLKeabxd403TGEmtLgmw9fzwm3QNfInWerwjteoXmtxOJN3c0_ptDHLOadYrY7ZX9q_Ry5psRAbX6vhlMRPGH8N3a-7PZ_pmMGr57ElX-V0Aa6xt_s6_7lCdFEpfpfxVhGc1gnOH8fqc6CQcubH1xSmhebgbTNsGIGAbZwezXkb9_uP9cYwmB0w1lMZnH5L8Rd8rhiDdBXCB3ueindCn1yThQy4wkY_WcGabe6_K1TAzFvyiiLOV8b7m911IJPU_Pvcw2ysVznc0EPt_yHGUM91Px7A%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;尽管华尔街支持特朗普&lt;/a&gt;，但也未能逃脱共和党的愤怒。在演讲中，特朗普试图将矛头指向摩根大通和美国银行，在没有证据的情况下指责它们限制接触他所称的“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgccsAQyXlzWLp0KHIg0AezZ15BjVa3HqQMrVSxj9ZPoICZYo4DkcK8B3Dby9JLh_Cpf5ZwHn2mciAzoYPTeZEiG2Oma5BFiH1x090MWI_G0YW1jkWmnKjr5fmQDs01pk4xIZ43v0Y5bglxovSdYhlfJUsGdO1hfvJQpAkSZe7l9uWL5-Jm26i73JsbWWC5t0uw-eSF7yokuRKcsoDnnQY8MG9SdQZ_W-2zXp1aa0o4lqcSmYEp_Ghp3FTKvSG0-Gy4LGNjpOfu0OM-wA0YN0mQX-P1T6kczKUCRtTTjnAjh9UKmPL6uLTl7gnh8PBtYu7NQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;保守派&lt;/a&gt;”客户，而银行认为这是谎言。然而，在美国大规模杀戮不断发生的背景下，银行限制了对一些枪支制造商的贷款。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; 2018 年初佛罗里达州一所高中发生枪击事件后，美国银行此前限制了向生产非军事用途突击型枪支的公司提供&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcQZgZxg_Eji9xZwUNEM3_FLV0JYzxKUBnUy4QiBs9FB6OZsjvIe7saejaGiM8tbkuFVcPJLYbpF6NxWvVEFIV-uaF0F7rouC9Q0ff3qwmmyXMiSzSbEN9LCz7SHoBsBUqi1BKhD5o1DjSWqz82CyXoxXqnAijU51ETGHDOnC97DHQdOb7dYWfJFmvdzmAf10HxHWOHJfPzey_k0HsfpnDAQRCt6TKOI6E7z02r723E0lyk0P0k9MhLJmUshS24EyZMxXX7hvLFt_CLBQPlvfG9orTFGTeZbUR6-BxYzhFL5HfsMeYKPg6WjLoDFfq_aRhw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;贷款&lt;/a&gt;。花旗集团当年也宣布了针对销售枪支的客户的一系列&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcWBHQO9T3WZSMODZ4crcPt0Ap3TFFjRFivcrzdB0IegmedyJ42X7PodxEMetHka_c0vZF6Gq1R0iWbWg0wLL5MhDAqzUnwpjVmMBlwG6R35GGghnR-Ar2quZfWUrz_7xjE3Nvsm5p4x3FI1GxMka6T9wu29HFtnvgNm-7bW3vSPtwKXz-dz2jZar7d6ZSvcqpwCIHcqFWjzF9hhgrmXXrIS-72dFIN6nZAbYXsQmIU6WJ3I7a56ACscNhB2tuql0VSEHMU9VU9qTWybzgIC7M9e6WGhPsEu3-FiwCT2d1g1FkaTEc5GU9THpAnaesIvzO0DUuD8PA9dxB9RIUklDwiGPfIo2QYm-PPq6euUOq2RM3GiFYFD8N6U1ojAKq-twwu7lNZWWBQMMYooVp-KsTfxnhboYCiUm5CJsgROCQH95YPCk7QrIB_LSS85pm8ngiQwJF7Hc_PVIA9iQV_VhvKV1uZruwrRRbnVsUxwB-dMHplu4SqwcMISUuMxYU1bwcQ%3D%3D" target="_blank" title="政策声明链接"&gt;限制&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;em&gt;——玛格丽特·萨瑟林和乔丹·厄布&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;今天您需要了解什么&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;一名联邦法官阻止了&lt;/strong&gt;特朗普&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcaRkwcfH-0z7-6hIqjOGGt8ys7iIQqn4lKJWxZryG_IsnarygOJJhSDliK3Hxv2ihn9EmvoP1Vx7N5B-A2Zi6YYoYENnqbcP4kB6vFsYdGVI3DCc9OGRSoXxF3rnaASOzmkj2y6k99cLJBiYL_Cd-RKgoHbXCoqgR45YrNiLVhqlofKfs1KLjPFgEkeDdotk6mVeQJKuk4820AFOdsxN08Cu5BWP2Byhp7RlBXds_hlfiJea0ZHZnO_fxJSFphELZ8_vWiZPzhd70Gw-a3smrBUh8nc5W51FmagPdiVYg-i687Wi1f6X2jaF6EsQDwOq7w%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;终止与生俱来的公民身份&lt;/a&gt;的行政命令，这是根据美国宪法的简单语言和一个世纪的先例作出的普遍预期的裁决。美国地区法官 John Coughenour 的决定在全国范围内生效，将在 14 天内阻止政府采取任何措施执行特朗普的行政命令，届时随着诉讼的进行，可能会进行更长期的延迟。就在特朗普首次失败的几天前， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcYhJrWjFzX6-5J4TofsQO5ubkJ8o3TEzVO7uJFMIZTSf-OUYAoXUHYtY_SZFnovFxwVWI66NZXYU66C74xy34newVLzoPoHi3kIEW7Q5Rd6p0iurg2lihLyCnMo3Bcb2yy6jFGrLHPEsZDCjiEKQ1jGebqCPpUVlOlwbTbtNsjrMTcmO1SoiiRk0KSb1krO-Dg240NWKNh8acC2UCUXIFPn-awS7AfkFi-h5linb6IxymlSeTuZDccnkxQlkMeQMFWMWgrbGJdmnpTpyrIn6Ver9wN1730jpUD9DqIz9_rw49UrZhq7kFL9BluLplAAGbA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;民主党领导的各州就该措施起诉了&lt;/a&gt;他。据&lt;em&gt;美联社&lt;/em&gt;报道，库格努尔对特朗普的律师说：“这是一项公然违宪的命令。”&lt;em&gt;据美联社&lt;/em&gt;报道，这位由罗纳德·里根任命的法官表示，他不记得曾经见过这样的案件，所质疑的行动如此&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcaBYfTlIRQyttiC1WxfiO9iPcwymi0xU8coPCO84gc6NEWvML7AJeJkDq85NDn38SecZQ3KW5SKoiHQnsKsCKtvwSvXgRYu4sr3l8anZyRiSU_WITxkgFCjo21ohLQlyy6T8mYGX_EJekcwyWHxMXOZB5Z9kb0wyihcfOd7evNLjDMDZZkTNekxeG0cM4Yz-ZrQ67hYWFTfBmKjQ4EpXmcKRwK2Q60sdjKpkfPeMDSnulVTtrz4XyYTwlMo6yzvKmEF3OSzNxljMYKERf8OLgK6xlKZ5va6PXEghE9jaDMyjpIJyc79Q2cs0wU6D2y29acKHbMSOwMPQ_cZEeaKSwfHC3Jr9ULh7ZZMC9Acvxno2ZOMRLQ8avo8EoSj8xqfeDRtSyy2c_rX1ZcWD0-vLFwY4K-x7hqSLBoQWwOyRaMKdO7N2Pgc1xiuKQ7RLUxbh9tibJhGaZkvL6aNM-LfI9HyKaKAO8euyur_uagp3j1vJsdd0r6sThXDnQ6PCmk_FMWUgLKUmA98EFW6kf9LPYxjsiEA1Noh8HXszgOgpMevoHtY0wigiwrX1VHCPjNRb9gEFIiqQQ8TCaQwc80C5QBccTlkrmIxPajlfyT9YimImiSq100RLs5PdFB03HYg8rWRUsRENNHtlDoSKxXJq5nnSdT37WKXn4pZ5T3jzRtUX5CRXvtKRrWn2viMRnQqFCwNRESvAnuj09DI75aAHhvGEULYdaYw8E1c07rohJKjr25P5tuwuB_chXqhdqSzfQIWNX9qYf3lNhmpzgXU9DAz3uBKNKheiHJAOQHogqMXcAV2wqVHtDmrBidMnba5Ydj6cwoG1rKj2W481McFkpUt9iXlNHO0FIcOpQG-e_bHlSZcHMSItCmKNbDYYYEfTnhmESkrJqS1SLa2r02aVRIxma-v6ftUF4QeLw8zljcMmWyna4HPQBYpok2aeYjfPJlfy3up0E9It-_Wf9WsvJhpjNvyrVLIgxIk-DWPehcyXI_bWg_lskuRy4SlhvV_NE5G2gAJGyqH2GyyWOT5GCpZ4JubcBoNrQtmuxsIp7waS" target="_blank"&gt;明显违反了宪法&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;前有线电视主持人&lt;/strong&gt;皮特·赫格斯 (Pete Hegseth) &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcXR_SVrkrDqr9AfCOi2tlHjJ6w47Ce6LmgaCWwChlKqYJ8FNwstl_8bpPag35eYz98bDbrIuNSKv4ffwi3T3cHcRD9CUfHKvOlvgGe7tQpOSip_wkfG1yPq3aeH500hjPeRQRx4eJYpc0y8um_B96YzXNzeWeUGs7UvcCIKU5zWaP2jUau7KnErURnfzMIudqxQIeDlo4dQScuVOAkY8-mYOFeWCo_DGDpJ3yW6YLBuGOuxlONMl1jK0We-QJrq07xQ4OaUEsWMxZQQAIHyAZ4zwNJXFtqJzWmXUNGMpOF_t6eO_LU0cM4NZep-mk53rzg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;距离控制世界上最强大的军队之一又近了一步&lt;/a&gt;，此前参议院投票中，共和党多数派（ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcaBYfTlIRQyttiC1WxfiO9i7efVfInM-x6o76U2lvmTNiL-G07azXZ31evTUZVQDyrdvQTCI2JcluKX0pLuGtbHvVkoVcInbQGAXJ5WTI-i0QnqhGDc2hjE5seyPJGR7aoIabYAn-9nodeUD4sXgi7F2Prv-4H2gr_T_XHeSIGH4HqNcg5FjqANNi9QZLwivpLdg6q49njGDkuoIm96AcVg0dryn3Kbq4HgE7ZhXf5MUPzsaRsS65xBM5xOj895j84uvljX91wwmg9cWBXAnrWGalx8Rvv9ZFmctOzoxsL-PzIeM9JWTrPWPZL72kDKsDi4gT49u-QlZxxgV3MYOPYufEamO9-s8U2IyxCezLGlChyn9Y_olM2fVFkszJRIzNruZGF6PoxLnbqWnNI4cwTdiRkR9Lc75cBY94lIeVZ9bFtUd3gAIp40TzaD8X7qhyTUlPd7L-VmUeW4Izc20sX3C78OIGXIqSAsYOc0YUAJYim3E1P2u0RwY-bDgI91Nx7qWLtWVt4NAtHWIf3K6PlF7LGY4vHQ1wh5vELRcEaHxDiVIa5INmLDtfiBtwNwR_RtgC-fOuqRfzk-OkGW-Wp9T90NpfOPy0lAx6bBhnCKkIem0V-YUqatEhCDh5SF-ZfNGvyD3y2-bnEdEo-DSSG2gnNlqPlA7R5HTWmAyt1xUr5NlfCwQhAPIQbML2d9vxrlYpxZgm6ZH0Jv-M2Hf_ZJji2zEqKtRE4swisdYBBG_uhsvuaZQ3QVZ4h4z94Lm-m-NlZIRMvrNAiyJ1wxJ8erF8gSL60owVzBT6Rfanh4J1CRkOlcmNkFNSvaUvuBMf-uAR3haVT83LQEmQAL00OiYC0wFxApgOqwBe-5l5yty2hT2Qwc_l5rwSZKxLFcqh7KPwipmMVi8VNtSOL_HsqDGtHujLvs2VGshwK9tG1XB7xMqofcR4DgLNrcVf3lhgTyX0XDpzGWH0a_umd8tUM5NASUT1nQlhSTXK5NcCGmfy90XBA2I9XFpO0wwTn57Ya28KBhIoJBZCuTx--xGWYbpojml_yja0MCic1OHYuTC" target="_blank"&gt;减二&lt;/a&gt;）提前提名他为国防部长。赫格斯没有在政府或军队的高层经验，他是特朗普非正统的内阁职位人选中最具争议的人之一。赫格斯否认了自特朗普点名以来&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcaBYfTlIRQyttiC1WxfiO9hK5WckUtVHqdge2RcmPQ8P8rQmdIvYEnaMAVTNpqc4NJ8tn1K5EDvIDXITB0mif-lAVQ-5NAUbYTz9OQSs8xTkcxGvW_-uMvPNUWeUEbaw37lY8Lkp3vLsMHWCsT2JwouJB4saT_qE4nYsg26AHcqHgPCO3HmutQmTAXDKv8D8_QqdTtFUNu6C2A6kXtrCuIelEJANUcZUWllSggq9vpw45iAaAg_4wdhvdgxeRxY-ydSrdfyYbI0EJ5QvkpcBPUQYaqbUE3toaaT3AMqLAnqfytHhrFyvOeTBfNLuDEVuvreGXw__536aypR0ikaKevahd7oL4YMBC0ef2Xnb3yEImXule1ikES_N3Qk0klcVbLAF029SS9UCu64HBShrfANrsc_aayuDoWIe0JNrWHiYsF4STMadCB7gytYe9M-Ta_Gg0jYX04Kyhf8JzVsDUIkhatQaZ1EgbZ3pQQrLHREL46J8ZjBgkwroZ-4DrGKcvzl9kO8x9Q7PTeOAUdYhOng%3D" target="_blank"&gt;不断&lt;/a&gt;出现的针对他的指控，从家庭暴力到酗酒等。尽管有新的虐待前妻的指控，今天的投票还是进行了。赫格斯否认有任何不当行为。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ih8Sz9su0Otc/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ih8Sz9su0Otc/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt; 1 月 20 日唐纳德·特朗普总统就职典礼期间的 Pete Hegseth&lt;i&gt;摄影师：Shawn Thew/EPA&lt;/i&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;洛杉矶的一场新火灾&lt;/strong&gt;， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgccbRM5lhrtGGHg3MB5765HosV-29rTK1NA-FILkG15_hHGTLbPEY3t5sdquVSWeTCpd2ZjPJSw5iseP1gu0ng5_aqKkayvGole_DcRrCODkKTMKMKslRiUfykXX1Y72CDiQSdHG7T7G4i6MfS6s2uMElJLxq8AJNDzt3BaTJpQrgHnbixpfXXkTXhyz7d5v5ftbF-TD9JD2xUe884jCtm8Zoh1Zh77MjDBr2z63py99wHRbtl-UnUbT_KC3nxsVyIY7qu1u3lHRjflqsLbzwAPmQQ9CMrOAXa9PubaptinhGh63KgHs7P3ee97hY5xrW1pHqGpnuy5gKKo1tAmpdGVuHBaQMTSSz8aX_RtPmqSduQU-cUpYLZw8Ufu0ztj3FZKwuY_DOR9FWux7Jl4R1-xo%3D" target="_blank"&gt;塞普尔维达火灾&lt;/a&gt;，于今天早些时候在盖蒂中心艺术博物馆和该市富裕的贝莱尔社区附近开始。至少 45 英亩的土地被烧毁，但洛杉矶消防局表示 60% 的面积已得到控制。另一起发生在文图拉县的拉古纳火灾也于今天开始， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcaB9_aWjfRc1Fd0o-I_Ctpp19Czeo_rolL_A7yFNgt_jj9lNCVTsS1BHqng5X8uydhbi7rXAJ-s77RSiKYkTfba2ifwSWLGnKekVDV4U2aNqspiHCI0TM-XgMTlBmmWaw5Yx1OLbrFAmJWEY3qGiP5H3yeQOxPkrZaKcbVxshy9COKCYXJXuJ6haIs5F9oYkIvBdBupjy83RxlehWbI_OmeTsEblO7MFpaxBjQ80fuPz0xRTtSHDMShZRziRxfkIrJsNPqGUwE0FqmqaDzIlc4G1OzfB9Krwv4LaZLqZi5pJEzawnIVziv38r9o2__owtQHGk4VWlo90D4OlaLDtrmJtm6XKwLmaYf-j6EqsUcl8bRzKvOE-AsXW_gC_B4eqwA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;到中午估计烧毁了 15 英亩的&lt;/a&gt;土地，促使加州州立大学海峡群岛分校疏散。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcS3DyLLIiRpBlAIuKi3Az4hJPuYoet_cXIkwKb8_1U7QqcaqphitVF7y76UuNAEDHYYQ-4ddLa3zbldZUooY5GgMaIWE0aYMz2MUu8UEh6TvAkDPY66YfBxrtYYtPNN7uwMkJuqTbsOQ7uN4QUSPkpryzaTFf7Xb7pCUFNNqPIksaIsw5XsB0CkOHviv9_qONzM0GyExTnBEnbQ3JflPkIrPqFg5sLJggH15WlMlGA0cIdfqjtkz2Z8qywW7W29UOinVsUtbmTT4K-f1OAWFdF7VEhMmC2vQf9GHjv-RIZvLcJsW6TBZSXlj3xqaWQQhNA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;今天的火灾&lt;/a&gt;是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcY-iYKsptfbNEditpZzNBfnrQtoLNd_7wY_VFu6u8-zAkSRbPopUibv1irYeGod2xQCnZYRiwvt27SgHtmDOGmyH-aAqTk7w0osXGmHa0YsxpXCn4o6WAmYXYmRhubCqKrtBYkfqjfk-6l8evyOcEPv8gPYaHnvUWfTOTlyJRpzc-gQPgRECuTgPudBFS_TEGbfbrm6J4ItVnIdVh1osdrqmGh9S62i_EVzXCG92We2oTZPoxs8-2am-8QsRB3XCwDWlRXceXlcqmAt3WzFjOa1ACKadBRUYmTpOxeThT3FV1cGQyk-ObFvrhB8NjiFcBA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;休斯火灾的补充，休斯&lt;/a&gt;火灾于周三开始，数小时内蔓延，面积超过 10,000 英亩（4,000 公顷）。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;美国抵押贷款利率自 12 月中旬以来首次下降&lt;/strong&gt;。房地美在一份声明中表示，30 年期贷款平均利率从上周的 7.04% &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcchcyRXxeVFY-esc8p6LCatnVTskh1bviuNKP5scX7og0BonxMKlM6Zqg0qTX6pfkPX1eEfn3qhVMCVoLInEP657rYKPwvyNs4ioIIfAR2BhEPCTjoa9Pgv6kgpN2s_BXV6UfdMW8SxME1_SacIRLtJbPsAXSW5iIWrDoNPNZIsRWRVcvX3ovq2GGkhkEuE-BPGz-jpmwnl05JdyOnQhLVhTyGfpaA-3kTY4k0tOf3wpb9HXHK9XGt8sjGBqriTlrWfl0AvBVITrUbw_6AaXLEJRtyiAzm8sYibRutTktZ5rimNBH4yL2LEKGGGcpNaYTQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;下滑至 6.96%&lt;/a&gt; 。虽然房价下跌可能有助于缓解潜在购房者的担忧，但他们仍然面临负担能力的挑战——借贷成本徘徊在接近数月来的最高水平，而&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcReKmLbAY1N1vqQJ3Cw_j-SCdsrfMIds82Gj3NNNgYUVC5rgoZtvBlQby3dd1447jniCg8icI8rYM35EQcbda3jvfckKLQsTj-uSZfBwUC4HDYJFtxEDhSX3Qbxid_mXtQl9xhIkHUAFvA725ibqTrFpp9DCuFa62KzScp5HNVpZasKnztfpjAhBHIqO7WWmolqEcZcIjauhNWQylxZA7fXccOiO1JPyTw5Hm-MsGRQc2KwyUyoqT_ok6HSTvBygB2w6tRamtDs6eR9z18W3-g65PbWE5i-J4TKHFEtNk8PvWBvp8PfvcfGGHAd8mcKKgimQ9Ugyxx84BtuYvind6p_-hSM_Gnb1blwprB6O3AAEy7ufLiyvV6cn33r8mdVRiXfeg3JM_nfU8Hi9ljnoxeQ%3D" target="_blank"&gt;购买价格仍在持续上涨&lt;/a&gt;。 Redfin 表示，购房者正在撤退，使得房产&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcReKmLbAY1N1vqQJ3Cw_j-TvdjWLcAqMVYJETbOym_XMoqWsgc2F3hrQAnUXtKH8n7q208rocIoqNzOikrpco9F6QIvSNhc7WsM5cB17guVwzoEzAQYVdmtA0le39GQ9E6v7Z1Hsgdx8jb3R2cgvFfrCO9IdoEGRm0ExyQlEgAeGSkPbXDIs7gOE-omewPatOITs37t0qeQYWQ7m9ql2TYMw2P8qCEL2lclNnya49_pmxOcKT0zEsC7F4Lgw6LM_CLawefJ_NUm1MAYRKpBE_VwaPcuRodEQEbqZnFWSaSa7FvQmZJEC0Gk1634jaAMOhI3PaJ1xswISdtCfuCLUv_d5cCVkRMwHh382j_h5doAnsi-rTZQS6MGoYbqLcZAdDJINEc32SHXUgcT1H_1NaWQJnKYU3mZtz20uWYiNr6QSyZwqTWWIpGXv5FenhQQ_fG8kas6VuIiA17r78UtjZvR-rh5_ixaYyEHolr2QUdb6" target="_blank"&gt;在市场上停留&lt;/a&gt;的时间更长。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;沙特阿拉伯王储穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼&lt;/strong&gt;告诉特朗普，他愿意在未来四年内将与美国的投资和贸易扩大&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcaX3LXLcxPyEIsTYrqk_BKIv3-itIw4gOi39iK8f5naYXTxdLxtcHTdYYN9DrPEAxnNVZwCZ4t7yfTIrBuzn6wAxfwuWNEbNjt2vDraIv8i3rxQqqiZCm61sN_ytCuI2jQu50p0iBPeER3uUCC25sWSjNdW6Tr5Tn8dmpwzAsJLPp9jOb46NvaJ-wh_Ct4C1B1kJ8XgKjq2e1V71ptoJ5vJON-U1r6K396eoktVDdOR836oUBlHm6PK4QV0XuYF48JYRCiCiG-qMsIA4oUkP5uH_lsDjHxyfH181xT_az79TGqYbSfVsv1Sxxb0IdNnxnA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;6000亿美元&lt;/a&gt;。即使按照石油资源丰富的沙特阿拉伯的标准来看，这也是一个巨大的承诺，约占该国国内生产总值的 55%。与此同时，沙特也出现了财政赤字，这在很大程度上是由于王储的经济多元化计划“2030 年愿景”的巨额支出。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;普渡大学及其所有者就&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcT81hw8FPbbvBkK81KOu9WJgKzeiYx4dk69VtkkKnsrtLbtqLRvjk7irjxC8RN3FZjyC3x4TifnPQI81jTrXzs83MkOenQK1-odMr_88wcTRdfYxejxE2kWPF_GOcvcZDFzD9cR7twQp2U3s1VGbkFGe5zWEXQ2Dw0NQORaY6E1mc8ajq8U91c2SXkr1j7JUpERQ2dW1Efgsc07TBDz-P8iQKlxoMpQVdhYrUQ1-z9QEOnPFV1aSbxENJA833PpgSUgASwe-7L7aQXgU4bzxAOuzyfRLnmJM1lWkerWcnWxAlVpGIH12wKzL3mOle0-g8Q%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;奥施康定在阿片类药物流行中所扮演的角色&lt;/a&gt;达成了 74 亿美元的和解协议。这笔交易只是萨克勒家族和两党州总检察长小组激烈斗争的法律传奇中的最新转折。后者表示，普渡大学奥施康定止痛药的营销和销售加剧了导致数十万美国人死亡的毒瘾流行。此前，美国最高法院去年&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcYk57OTLW_TwkSVSZ92FJ16rDfNSjfI_pUSEkSpcR_HQTg9gH-vAf8JpjFfPiasTe3u6I-UkVz9qizPlHDLrX7BTB9or1I9o6gdsBFqvGFrzEOinzyau54R4jLkTCCbg-UaXjLR6F-41VJmfi7lCmBWxwEdxAjl8e5_VNh10TlnAhF0dy6Sl3SfMBoUrsHY5ttAdEVZf1gskgTQUGwo_tkD2GsClKsOBao09nEoZirAPXsSwc5KFc2PP2tdacZcezcjW4dopIZucYH_qoS-4qe7EQT5ZZeA5g9QCBVGQe_3WPpPKyKU6AWjq1QwvsPRJGw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;驳回了&lt;/a&gt;一项价值 60 亿美元的协议，该协议旨在保护普渡大学的所有者、亿万富翁家族的成员免受与毒瘾危机相关的任何进一步诉讼。纽约州总检察长利蒂西亚·詹姆斯在一份&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcfOHxN6JYvHe4nKZvC_i3jmifw8_pDxo_4d4c4hh-TCdTvbLI1mvzvtjt8_QB4yrdMgAJmB7eZN3zoXUwhEIqiuhm4Bx87rlX1kbhKpvZ-wXZFIY_H0Y7HaXRDANhO9x1gRtjFcfmAg99riOyxQ_QJSLH5G5SqSpULvbeH65h2NfhiM035o7qsMeICvqwz-PqaiB9bJP1VKWuXxbLeZn-w984SMFoOVVbMvHXBoRXMslt-IiyZDVFm8IybxY4-Yxv7nIHTWi2HoRedwjO9dOwYAalJ0NqjTZhQcyAg1ccbZvvlPEhQCT01V9-U9oiJAVy7et-MbFx5lnZO32xaDtnSGbMY0Cj6h2XELkn032yPac74w2quA0ONwuZCstAq8lOW0OWjVPA_9bye0fV7xBQTCvS2zfSXKn3ur_4VTV650Y-JXuW3Jnp3wqEK3xSa9Xpt3gBT0TRRsNBaHe51QtjXUojgqj8LRWYEufrT7TFYm1c4taUif36qkNHjRvnyRi39VrTZ4XPvvO_Usi7mcDvyWH8NzT_7mb2RmQr3FK7E4J" target="_blank"&gt;声明&lt;/a&gt;中表示，今天的和解原则上不会自动保护该家庭免受未来诉讼的影响。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top